creator: Asia Medical Payments
descriptionHtml:
AMP’S SEAMLESS DIGITAL PAYMENT FACILITATES:

MANAGE YOUR MONEY
1. Payment data for you to track your expenditure.
2. Seamless top-up via PayNow or Bank Transfer
3. Currencies supported are SGD and USD. We will integrate more currencies soon. Stay tuned!
4. Send money to China or any UnionPay card users in 60 secs.

TRAVEL AND SHOPPING
1. No longer that you have to exchange your local currency to Chinese Yuan whenever you travel in China. Just top-up via PayNow or bank transfer and pay like the local whenever you are in China. It is just as seamless.
2. Best exchange rate of Chinese Yuan.
3. World -wide acceptance in 41 million merchants on 179 countries.
4. Enjoy UnionPay International rebates at airports, duty free outlets and shopping malls.

PAY GLOBALLY
1. Worldwide acceptance of virtual UnionPay cards
2. Now you can shop and pay seamlessly on and off-line globally and that include e-commerce sites in China

SECURED & REGULATED
1. If you lose your phone, just login into your desktop and freeze your virtual card. If you find it again, just unfreeze your card
2. The safety of your money is of our upmost priority. As a Principle Member of UnionPay International, all your transactions are therefore processed and protected by UnionPay's International rules and standards.
3. We are regulated by Monetary Authority of Singapore, under the Payments Services Act.
4. With our Dynamic QR code, we have in-built security features into our app to help detect and prevent fraud payments to fake merchants.


While, initially the focus is on Singapore, expanding services to another 10 countries by 2022, is the next goal.

The countries are : Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, Philippines, Dubai, Thailand, France, United Kingdom, South Korea, Australia and Georgia.

The ultimate user experience will combine ease and convenience as clients effortlessly choose from a global array of trusted medical professionals and healthcare groups.

All our business partners are distinguished entities, carefully chosen to include the most respected and experienced medical professionals, leading hospitals, and specialised healthcare groups.

AMP’s medical partners are reputed for their long years of experience, enviable success rates, and highest professionalism in all aspect of patient care.

All our business partners are distinguished entities, carefully chosen to include the most respected and experienced medical professionals, leading hospitals, and specialised healthcare groups.

AMP’s medical partners are reputed for their long years of experience, enviable success rates, and highest professionalism in all aspect of patient care.

title: Asia Medical Payments

creator: Asia Medical Payments
descriptionHtml:
AMP’S SEAMLESS DIGITAL PAYMENT FACILITATES:

MANAGE YOUR MONEY
1. Payment data for you to track your expenditure.
2. Seamless top-up via PayNow or Bank Transfer
3. Currencies supported are SGD and USD. We will integrate more currencies soon. Stay tuned!
4. Send money to China or any UnionPay card users in 60 secs.

TRAVEL AND SHOPPING
1. No longer that you have to exchange your local currency to Chinese Yuan whenever you travel in China. Just top-up via PayNow or bank transfer and pay like the local whenever you are in China. It is just as seamless.
2. Best exchange rate of Chinese Yuan.
3. World -wide acceptance in 41 million merchants on 179 countries.
4. Enjoy UnionPay International rebates at airports, duty free outlets and shopping malls.

PAY GLOBALLY
1. Worldwide acceptance of virtual UnionPay cards
2. Now you can shop and pay seamlessly on and off-line globally and that include e-commerce sites in China

SECURED & REGULATED
1. If you lose your phone, just login into your desktop and freeze your virtual card. If you find it again, just unfreeze your card
2. The safety of your money is of our upmost priority. As a Principle Member of UnionPay International, all your transactions are therefore processed and protected by UnionPay's International rules and standards.
3. We are regulated by Monetary Authority of Singapore, under the Payments Services Act.
4. With our Dynamic QR code, we have in-built security features into our app to help detect and prevent fraud payments to fake merchants.
